Bush Industries Inc said itexpects higher earnings and sales for 1987, partly due toefficiencies in manufacturing that have improved its margins.    The company reported first quarter earnings of 1,328,000dlrs, up from 344,000 dlrs a year before, on sales of 23.0 mlndlrs, up from 12.3 mln dlrs.  For all of last year it earned2,506,000 dlrs on sales of 65.4 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;